      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 21:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大向特朗普表示：我们也对边境问题有抱怨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/canada-to-trump-we-have-complaints-about-the-border-too</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理表示，加强边境安全“符合加拿大人和美国人的利益”，并对从美国向北流动的非法枪支和毒品数量不断增加表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/canada-to-trump-we-have-complaints-about-the-border-too</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 21:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 的 Calvert 表示加密货币仍是特朗普的优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/crypto-is-still-a-trump-priority-coinbase-s-calvert-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Coinbase 美国政策主管 Kara Calvert 对特朗普总统就职演说中没有提到加密货币以及特朗普推出自己的 memecoin 后，表示 Coinbase 在考虑新上市时会努力保持“代币不可知论”。她与 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 在“Bloomberg Crypto”节目中进行了交谈。（来源：Bloomberg）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/crypto-is-still-a-trump-priority-coinbase-s-calvert-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 20:53:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国罢免反垄断监管机构主席以释放增长信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-ousts-chair-of-antitrust-watchdog-to-send-growth-signal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府罢免了英国反垄断监管机构竞争与市场管理局 (Competition and Markets Authority) 的主席，因为内阁大臣们试图强调他们希望监管机构采取更多措施促进经济增长的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-ousts-chair-of-antitrust-watchdog-to-send-growth-signal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 19:57:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普迷惑市场 关税推迟 股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/tesla-slides-space-stocks-soar-after-trump-s-barrage-of-orders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普第二任期开始一个交易日后，很明显股市有了新的驱动力，至少目前如此。周二股价上涨，涨幅主要源于总统没有做的一件事：对主要贸易伙伴实施全面关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/tesla-slides-space-stocks-soar-after-trump-s-barrage-of-orders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 18:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上任第一天安抚债券交易员并压低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/treasuries-rally-on-first-trading-day-under-trump-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们对唐纳德·特朗普扩张性的促增长政策议程可能带来的后果感到担忧，但美国国债市场开局平稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/treasuries-rally-on-first-trading-day-under-trump-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
